00:42:42,000 --> 00:42:43,470
Ai đấy?

700
00:42:49,840 --> 00:42:50,540
Chết tiệt

701
00:42:50,680 --> 00:42:52,370
Gì vậy, Conan?

702
00:42:52,510 --> 00:42:55,100
Bác ơi, cháu nghĩ Ran-neechan có thể đã thấy

703
00:42:55,100 --> 00:42:58,410
mặt hung thủ khi hắn bắn chị Saito

704
00:42:58,550 --> 00:42:59,410
Sao?!

705
00:42:59,550 --> 00:43:00,640
